<span id="freeTextContainer4670702175642179342">Wilson’s dialog is superb. The conflict is all too real. The prose is strong, realistic with some poetic smatterings scattered about. Vibrant, with an emotional pull causing the narrative and ensemble to come alive. The building tension creates a suspenseful and plausible ambiance.<br/><br/>The ending adds fuel to the fire, as the climatic finale binds the entire narrative.</span>

