<ul>
<li class='cover' id='bookCover_59024462'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/59024462-betrayal-at-the-border"><img alt="Betrayal at the Border" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1632036603l/59024462._SX98_.jpg" />
